Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.02,0:00:04.86,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,I think I'll go see a movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.28,0:00:06.57,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,How about you, Kugisaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.57,0:00:09.74,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,It's still early. I'll go shopping or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.74,0:00:11.78,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,You guys are so full of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.78,0:00:13.74,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,I'm going home, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.87,0:00:16.16,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.37,0:00:20.04,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,All right, moving on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.00,0:00:23.71,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,I'm going to the movies. What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.17,0:00:25.59,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,What are you watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.59,0:00:27.05,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\i1}Human Earthworm 4{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.05,0:00:28.26,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Who even watches that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.26,0:00:30.89,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,I haven't even seen parts 1, 2, or 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.89,0:00:33.26,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,I think you'd be fine jumping in on 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.35,0:00:40.31,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,The mad scientist from the first movie, Dr. Richter,\N is making his long-awaited comeback!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.93,0:00:41.27,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,{\an8}No! Stop! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.31,0:00:46.15,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,And the human-earthworm hybrids born from his experiments\N are gonna create an enhanced Human Earthworm!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.15,0:00:47.82,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,What the hell? That's so gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.44,0:00:52.32,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,The poor Human Earthworm barely escaped Dr. Richter,\N and after a lot of wandering,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.32,0:00:56.20,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,ended up at a campground\N where a group of college students arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.20,0:00:58.54,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,That's when the real story kicks off.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.54,0:01:03.46,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,You see, among that group is a kind girl\N who is an animal welfare advocate,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.46,0:01:06.09,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,and the Human Earthworm falls in love with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.63,0:01:09.47,Default,Humanearthworm,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,0)}I'm not a human anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.47,0:01:11.84,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,You're more human than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.09,0:01:13.47,Default,Man,0,0,0,,It's a monster! Kill it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.47,0:01:14.89,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,Kevin, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.89,0:01:16.64,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,If we kill him, then we're the monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.60,0:01:21.35,Default,BabyHumanEarthworm,0,0,0,,Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.35,0:01:23.48,Default,BabyHEWs,0,0,0,,{\an8}Daddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.35,0:01:23.48,Default,BabyHEWs,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.35,0:01:23.48,Alt,BabyHEWs,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.11,0:01:28.23,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,So the theme is actually love!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.49,0:01:35.78,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,I don't wanna see some wormo man,\N regardless of the theme.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.53,0:01:38.20,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,It's Human Earthworm, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.20,0:01:40.16,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.16,0:01:42.79,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,I'm going shopping, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.29,0:01:44.50,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Wanna come with?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.50,0:01:47.05,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,I just said I'm going to the movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.05,0:01:48.30,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.30,0:01:49.55,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Later, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.47,0:02:04.52,Default,Gakuganji,0,0,0,,The rank of special grade is\N somewhat misrepresented among sorcerers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.52,0:02:12.24,Default,Gakuganji,0,0,0,,I believe it's the first-grades who uphold\N the standards and lead the world of sorcery.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.24,0:02:18.16,Default,Gakuganji,0,0,0,,The danger, confidentiality, and compensation \Nthat come with it are unlike anything below that grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.16,0:02:21.41,Default,Gakuganji,0,0,0,,With that in mind, can you repeat yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.75,0:02:24.29,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Zenin Maki, Panda...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.29,0:02:30.46,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,...Fushiguro Megumi, Kugisaki Nobara,\N and my brother, Itadori Yuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.46,0:02:33.55,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,These are the five that I, by my name as Todo Aoi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.55,0:02:36.01,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,...and I, by my name as Mei Mei
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.01,0:02:38.89,Default,Both,0,0,0,,recommend for first grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.89,0:02:45.56,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,Those recommended by at least two first-grades
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.56,0:02:52.61,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,must carry out missions under an active first-grade,\N or a first-grade equivalent sorcerer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.36,0:02:59.62,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,After that, if they're deemed fit,\N they'll be promoted to semi-first grade
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.62,0:03:03.33,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,and assigned first-grade missions\N to complete independently.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.33,0:03:10.09,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,The results of those missions will decide whether or not\N they'll officially become first-grade sorcerers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.96,0:03:14.30,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,My brother will no doubt accept the recommendation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.30,0:03:16.26,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,Since Sukuna isn't cooperating,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.26,0:03:21.76,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,he'll need to be assigned more dangerous missions\N to raise his chances of finding the fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.76,0:03:25.73,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,You understand what that means, right, Miss Mei? {alright i'll have to change every instance of Mei to Miss Mei now}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.77,0:03:32.61,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,It means exactly what it sounds like, Mister Todo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.95,0:03:44.54,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,A bright future... {literally untranslatable}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.54,0:03:51.88,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,In other words, a future where Todo Aoi and Itadori Yuji\N face missions together lies ahead of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.42,0:03:54.01,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,That's what it means!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.30,0:03:54.92,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:56.55,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,No need to spell it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.55,0:03:59.68,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,The sorcerer who accompanies him may not be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.68,0:04:01.47,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,Is that what you were saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:03.60,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,But there is no doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.60,0:04:08.94,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,Just like apple from a tree falls to the ground,\N the two of us are drawn to each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.90,0:04:14.53,Default,Todo,0,0,0,,Yes, it is indeed destiny. {alpha time?}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.82,0:04:17.49,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,No, what I was saying is
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.49,0:04:23.04,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,the sorcerers who put in the recommendation\N can't be assigned to accompany him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.91,0:04:31.00,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Since we're the ones who recommended Itadori{**-kun},\N someone else will be accompanying him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.83,0:04:32.96,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,It was a good match.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.96,0:04:35.92,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I'll be leaving now, Mister Todo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.39,0:04:48.52,Default,Ozawa,0,0,0,,Um, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.44,0:04:55.57,Default,Ozawa,0,0,0,,You were with Itadori{**-kun} just now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.03,0:04:59.03,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Uh...
Comment: 0,0:04:59.03,0:04:59.07,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Opening}
Comment: 0,0:06:28.95,0:06:28.99,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:34.04,Default,Waitress,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.42,0:06:37.75,Default,Ozawa,0,0,0,,This is me at our middle school graduation ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.75,0:06:41.17,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Wait, what?! That was only six months ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:43.05,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,What happened to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.05,0:06:47.39,Default,Ozawa,0,0,0,,Well, I've grown about 15 centimeters since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:51.93,Default,Ozawa,0,0,0,,And with moving to Tokyo and \Nthe stress of changing environments...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.93,0:06:53.94,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.94,0:06:56.31,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,You're a real Sato Kuroko. {yuyu hakusho}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:06:58.82,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,That's Itadori.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.82,0:07:03.03,Default,Ozawa,0,0,0,,On graduation day, I worked up the courage\N to ask for a photo with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.03,0:07:06.32,Default,Ozawa,0,0,0,,I actually wanted to get his number too,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.32,0:07:09.20,Default,Ozawa,0,0,0,,but it was already decided \Nthat I would be moving to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.83,0:07:12.33,Default,Ozawa,0,0,0,,So when I saw Itadori{**-kun} earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.83,0:07:16.75,Default,Ozawa,0,0,0,,I thought maybe with how I look now, I might...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.75,0:07:17.88,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.88,0:07:20.34,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Yuko, does that mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.55,0:07:22.21,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,It's like {\i1}that{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.42,0:07:24.47,Default,Ozawa,0,0,0,,Yes! It's like {\i1}that{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.34,0:07:28.76,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Hey, {*}Mr. Ijichi{*Ijichi-san}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.76,0:07:30.64,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Is Fushiguro still in the car with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.64,0:07:32.81,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,I sent you the location of the restaurant I'm at.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.81,0:07:35.02,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Could you turn around and drop him here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.02,0:07:37.10,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Alright! Thanks a bunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.73,0:07:41.86,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Someone who knows Itadori well\N is on his way here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.86,0:07:42.78,Default,Ozawa,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.78,0:07:44.86,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Let's start with hearing what he has to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.86,0:07:45.99,Default,Ozawa,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.66,0:07:50.37,Default,Ozawa,0,0,0,,If you're also interested in Itadori{**-kun}...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.37,0:07:51.37,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.95,0:07:55.00,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Even if heaven and earth were to dance the lambada.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.00,0:07:56.25,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Not happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.88,0:08:03.13,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's this weird feeling in my chest?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.13,0:08:04.59,Default,Kugisaki & Screen,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did my heart just skip a beat? {arrhythmia}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.09,0:08:10.14,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,All right, what's the big idea? {>yo}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.14,0:08:11.85,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,'Sup, Fushiguro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.85,0:08:13.60,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Does Itadori have a girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.60,0:08:14.47,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.47,0:08:16.14,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,This is Ozawa Yuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.81,0:08:19.56,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,She's actually something, something,\N and something like...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.69,0:08:21.56,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,So it's like {\i1}that{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.61,0:08:23.82,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's like {\i1}that{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.28,0:08:26.19,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,I doubt he has a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.19,0:08:27.45,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,What makes you think that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.45,0:08:31.07,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,He didn't seem particularly upset\N about moving to Tokyo all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.82,0:08:34.45,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,And he's got one of those posters hanging in his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.45,0:08:37.96,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,Anyone with a girlfriend wouldn't put up\N something like that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.96,0:08:39.33,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,She wouldn't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.33,0:08:43.75,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Are you the type who drinks coffee black\Naround girls just to show off?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:44.42,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Please don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.42,0:08:47.72,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,Are you forgetting why you called me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.72,0:08:49.18,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,And I always drink it black.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.01,0:08:53.56,Default,Ozawa,0,0,0,,Um, by the way, do you happen to know what's his type?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.06,0:08:57.85,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,I think he mentioned he likes tall girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.27,0:09:02.98,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,You've got a shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.98,0:09:04.52,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,I'm gonna summon Itadori!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.52,0:09:06.48,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,You're okay with that, right, Yuko?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.48,0:09:07.61,Default,Ozawa,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.45,0:09:14.83,Default,Ozawa,0,0,0,,That was curt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.41,0:09:16.33,Default,Kugiasawa,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.08,0:09:18.96,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Oh, Fushiguro is here too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.96,0:09:20.21,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,That was fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.17,0:09:23.46,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.46,0:09:24.25,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,{\an8}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.25,0:09:26.84,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}I never told him about Yuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.96,0:09:28.21,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\an8}Finding a cash exchange was a pain,\N so I traded in for prizes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.46,0:09:30.72,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no way he would recognize her\N after she's changed so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.22,0:09:34.18,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,120)}Who're you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.85,0:09:41.10,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's the last thing you wanna hear when reuniting with the person you adore!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.10,0:09:42.02,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Itadori!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.02,0:09:42.85,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,This girl is{\fscx180}—{\fscx}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.02,0:09:42.85,Alt,Yuji,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.85,0:09:44.40,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,It's Ozawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.40,0:09:45.57,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,How did you end up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.78,0:09:49.03,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,What a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.65,0:09:54.91,Default,Student,0,0,0,,Okay, so which girl in our class do you like, Itadori?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.21,0:10:05.00,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,999)}None of them, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.00,0:10:07.21,Default,Student,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,999)}What if you {\i1}had{\i0} to pick one!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.92,0:10:09.09,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,999)}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.09,0:10:12.01,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,999)}If I had to pick, then, Ozawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.68,0:10:14.22,Default,Student,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,999)}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.22,0:10:17.43,Default,Student,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,999)}No way, man. She's fat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.64,0:10:20.85,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,999)}I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.85,0:10:24.60,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,999)}But have you noticed her eating manners\N and her handwriting and stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.60,0:10:26.40,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,999)}I find it really pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.82,0:10:32.70,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(960,75)}It's super hard to eat fish properly, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.70,0:10:36.91,Default,Student,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(960,75)}I thought you said you liked tall girls with big butts? {this question and its response seems very similar to ep15 and i would've used the same lines but the phrasing is actually different in jp}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.91,0:10:38.91,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(960,75)}That's a different thing entirely!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.66,0:10:47.04,Default,Ozawa,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,990)\i1}It's easy for girls to get fat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.42,0:10:49.71,Default,Ozawa,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,999)\i1}I was always fat, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.88,0:10:52.38,Default,Student,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(960,75)}Why not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.38,0:10:53.34,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(960,75)}Nah, I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.34,0:10:56.39,Default,Student,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(960,75)}You should come with us, Itadori!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.39,0:10:57.80,Default,Student,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(960,75)}Let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.18,0:11:02.89,Default,Ozawa,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,999)\i1}But even I have no intention of \Nchoosing someone who won't choose me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.49,0:11:19.37,Default,Ozawa,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,999)\i1}Itadori{**-kun} was looking at a side of me I wasn't aware of.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.12,0:11:23.91,Default,Ozawa,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,999)\i1}I hated all the boys except him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.54,0:11:26.25,Default,Ozawa,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.38,0:11:33.30,Default,Ozawa,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,999)\i1}"Maybe with how I look now, I might..."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.01,0:11:40.68,Default,Ozawa,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,999)\i1}I'm living by the same standards as the people I hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.39,0:11:47.27,Default,Student,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,999)}Later, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.27,0:11:47.90,Default,Student,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,999)}See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.90,0:11:48.65,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,999)}Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.86,0:11:52.44,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,See you around!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.46,0:12:11.04,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,Was that really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.04,0:12:13.13,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,They could've at least exchanged numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.13,0:12:16.51,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,She exchanged hers with me, so yeah, it'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.93,0:12:20.89,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,More importantly, Fushiguro,\N I've finally realized my own feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.89,0:12:21.68,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.68,0:12:26.89,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,The idea of Itadori getting a girlfriend\N before I get a boyfriend really pisses me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.89,0:12:28.06,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.06,0:12:29.56,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.85,0:12:31.56,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Walk behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:33.69,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Hm? What's this?\N What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.69,0:12:34.90,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.90,0:12:36.24,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Oh? Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.24,0:12:37.03,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.03,0:12:39.36,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Uh-huh. What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.36,0:12:40.70,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,While you're at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.70,0:12:41.41,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,While I'm at it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.41,0:12:44.99,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you feel bad making a lady carry them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.70,0:12:47.91,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.91,0:12:50.92,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Oh, shoot! The movie's about to start! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.92,0:12:53.00,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Hey! Hold up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.00,0:12:54.42,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Don't take my stuff with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.42,0:12:53.00,Alt,Yuji,0,0,0,,Come on, come on, come on. Gotta hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.42,0:12:56.59,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,There's no way I'm watching some wormo man!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.59,0:12:58.42,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,You wanna grab some popcorn, Fushiguro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.42,0:12:59.55,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,You like caramel flavor, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.55,0:13:02.14,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,Don't just assume we're going to watch wormo man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.14,0:13:05.10,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\an8}I told you all it's {\i1}Human Earthworm 4{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:13:05.97,0:13:06.02,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.08,0:13:27.50,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.50,0:13:30.00,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,A curse user might be one thing, but cursed spirits? {adding "Working with..." might help but will be inconsistent with the original line} {she doesn't say that in jp, the viwers are expected to remember this kek}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.00,0:13:33.79,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,Plenty of high-level ones have been popping up lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.79,0:13:37.34,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,120)}This person might only be \Nin contact with a curse user, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.63,0:13:41.63,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,0)}I'd like you to investigate the Kyoto school, Utahime.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.85,0:13:46.93,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.39,0:13:50.98,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,Gojo informed you all about the mole, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.44,0:13:52.56,Default,Three,0,0,0,,{\pos(825,1020)}Yes.                   Yes.                   Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.56,0:13:55.73,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,We think there are two or more people\Nin contact with the curse users.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.73,0:13:58.23,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,One would be a higher-up, well above the principal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.23,0:14:00.74,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,I won't be able to do anything about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.15,0:14:05.24,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,The other would be someone \Nfeeding information to that higher-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.74,0:14:07.54,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,That's our current target.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.99,0:14:11.92,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,They're only a suspect at this point,\N so our objective is to capture and interrogate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.42,0:14:14.67,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,So who from Kyoto is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.67,0:14:15.34,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Uh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.75,0:14:19.51,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Why else would they involve us Tokyo students?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.51,0:14:21.30,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Kugisaki, you're a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.68,0:14:26.43,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,The mole is{\fscx180}—{\fscx}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.43,0:14:28.14,Default,Miwa,0,0,0,,Mechamaru! {meme this?}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.51,0:14:29.97,Default,Miwa,0,0,0,,Oh, there you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.52,0:14:32.85,Default,Miwa,0,0,0,,Today's the last day to turn in your notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.23,0:14:38.57,Default,Miwa,0,0,0,,Mechamaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.36,0:14:41.28,Default,Mechamaru,0,0,0,,Sorry, Miwa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.28,0:14:42.74,Default,Mechamaru,0,0,0,,I'm going to sleep for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.28,0:14:46.91,Default,Mechamaru,0,0,0,,Please take the notebook from my desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.91,0:14:49.99,Default,Miwa,0,0,0,,Sleep? It's still only evening?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.16,0:14:54.54,Default,Miwa,0,0,0,,Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.92,0:15:00.63,Default,Miwa,0,0,0,,{\i1}He really did go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.63,0:15:03.42,Default,Miwa,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder where the real Mechamaru is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.22,0:15:09.89,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,The real Mechamaru, Muta Kokichi, is in this basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.81,0:15:15.14,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,Now, it's not that he is suspicious, \Nit's more like no one else is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.14,0:15:17.40,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,The process of elimination leaves us with Mechamaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.99,0:15:34.12,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,Mechamaru's technique is Puppet Manipulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.12,0:15:38.50,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,Thanks to his Heavenly Restriction,\N its range extends throughout all of Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.09,0:15:44.17,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,Unregistered puppets could very easily\N do the work of a mole.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.63,0:15:48.30,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,You think? It'd draw a lot of attention if you ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.30,0:15:51.56,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,Even if the puppet was as small as a mosquito?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.56,0:15:54.31,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. I guess that's an option too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.90,0:15:58.27,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,We're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.48,0:16:02.73,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,They've arrived?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.00,0:16:20.08,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.84,0:16:22.88,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,He got us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.88,0:16:24.38,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,Though, on the other hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.38,0:16:26.88,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Now we're certain it's Mechamaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.89,0:16:35.56,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.56,0:16:37.64,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,I thought you forgot about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.23,0:16:39.90,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,We wouldn't make a blunder like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.44,0:16:43.98,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,You know firsthand how terrifying a restriction can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.48,0:16:47.45,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,This place always stinks of mold. I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:51.16,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,He's an enemy now. Let's just kill him quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.62,0:16:53.99,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,You can't do that yet, Mahito.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.74,0:17:02.63,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,In exchange for his cooperation and information,\N we agreed to fix his body using your Idle Transfiguration.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.67,0:17:07.01,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,That's the Binding Vow we forged, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.26,0:17:10.76,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,Killing him comes after fixing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.22,0:17:16.31,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,He could've been useful in Shibuya, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.31,0:17:17.56,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,It's a real shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.23,0:17:20.90,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,"We won't lay a hand on anyone from the Kyoto school."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.90,0:17:24.07,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,You already broke that part of the Binding Vow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.07,0:17:26.23,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Hanami's the one who did that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.23,0:17:29.03,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,You shouldn't lash out at the wrong people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.03,0:17:31.32,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,I have no intention of debating with a curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.32,0:17:33.91,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,Hurry up and fix me, scum.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.41,0:17:39.66,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,I might go overboard and turn him into a caterpillar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.66,0:17:40.67,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,Mahito.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.67,0:17:45.67,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,A Binding Vow forged with others is very different\N from one that's placed upon oneself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.30,0:17:50.55,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,A key difference is the uncertain nature of the penalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.97,0:17:53.89,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,When you break a Binding Vow with yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.89,0:17:57.89,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,the worst that can happen\N is you lose the abilities that you gained.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.31,0:17:59.98,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,But this is a different case.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.98,0:18:06.40,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,If you break this Binding Vow, we'll have no idea when,\N or what kind of disaster might befall us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.40,0:18:07.98,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.82,0:18:11.70,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,You're lower than scum, so be grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.07,0:18:15.45,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Idle Transfiguration.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.86,0:18:50.28,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,You're no fun at all. Show some enthusiasm!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.49,0:18:55.24,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,I'll do that after I'm finished here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.95,0:18:58.45,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,I suppose that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.37,0:19:01.96,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Shall we get started, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.30,0:19:12.38,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,Need a hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.38,0:19:14.88,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,No way! He's {\i1}my{\i0} toy.
Comment: 0,0:19:19.01,0:19:19.81,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,There!
Comment: 0,0:19:23.89,0:19:25.14,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Take that!
Comment: 0,0:19:34.95,0:19:35.91,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.71,0:19:46.33,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,He ran away?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.21,0:19:50.42,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Well, it's not like he needs to kill us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.09,0:19:52.46,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,How boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.21,0:19:55.55,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,I don't feel like hunting. I just wanna fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.48,0:20:15.20,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Now that's more like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.45,0:20:26.33,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,To think that you were tinkering away\N at something like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.33,0:20:29.08,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Guess you put all that time as a shut-in to good use.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.67,0:20:31.34,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're inside, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.34,0:20:33.59,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't want me touching you, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.09,0:20:35.47,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}The cockpit...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.13,0:20:39.05,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1\fad(0,180)}The seat of his soul... is the head!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.72,0:20:41.18,Default,SystemVoice,0,0,0,,Amplification functions normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.18,0:20:43.01,Default,SystemVoice,0,0,0,,Sensory feedback blocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.01,0:20:45.56,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,Tch. They deployed a Veil.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.56,0:20:46.89,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,Must be Geto.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.85,0:20:52.02,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,It's not just trapping me inside. It's cutting off signal, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.27,0:20:56.03,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,This won't go as smoothly\N as it would have with Gojo Satoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.40,0:21:00.16,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right. My key to victory is Gojo Satoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.78,0:21:04.54,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,{\i1}I need to get in contact with Gojo Satoru\Nby any means necessary,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.54,0:21:06.87,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,{\i1}tell him about the Shibuya plot,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.87,0:21:08.50,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,{\i1}and have him rescue me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.04,0:21:12.67,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,{\i1}As much as I would like to focus on Geto,\N the one who deployed this Veil,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.67,0:21:14.75,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mahito is too dangerous to ignore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.30,0:21:17.26,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll have to exorcise him first.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.97,0:21:22.22,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,{\i1}Go ahead, don't mind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.81,0:21:25.47,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm still at a disadvantage,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.85,0:21:28.35,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I have a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.82,0:21:36.57,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have seen it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.90,0:21:40.32,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,{\i1}All those years I was tied down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.32,0:21:42.37,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,{\i1}All the cursed energy I stored over that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.99,0:21:44.99,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't hold anything back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.50,0:21:54.63,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,One-Year Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.63,0:21:57.30,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,Incinerate, Mechamaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.76,0:22:02.76,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,Ultra Cannon!
Comment: 0,0:22:09.98,0:22:10.02,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Ending}
Comment: 0,0:23:39.98,0:23:39.98,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Preview}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.65,0:23:44.03,Default,Miwa,0,0,0,,{\an8}If you want a secret to remain a secret,\N keep it to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.03,0:23:48.78,Default,Miwa,0,0,0,,{\an8}I wrote out what type of boy I like in my elementary school profile book and everyone found out!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.78,0:23:50.33,Default,Miwa,0,0,0,,{\an8}Next Episode, Evening Festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.33,0:23:51.45,Default,Mai,0,0,0,,{\an8}What did you write down?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.45,0:23:52.66,Default,Miwa,0,0,0,,{\an8}Mittermeyer. {from LOGH??}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.66,0:23:54.75,Default,Mai,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sure got that fast-runner vibe. {cause elementary school girls like fast guys}
